Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有這樣的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同玩笑一般不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼才能長得像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣嗎  像這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道她被媽媽給灌輸了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這事是絕對不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是真的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄…比呂美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是白癡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來不就是打算放棄的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了  上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我沒有食慾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有食慾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在煩惱著的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你一起想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過  如果我在身邊你就會混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我認為那是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混亂的原因反而是因為你孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在黑暗裡  只要有人相伴左右的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡一定能夠堅強起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能找到最終的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會成為真一郎的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎  說出來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把這個還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面  今天給你份意外的驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的吧  地面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天中午也不打算吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你便當
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別剩下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山芋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山芋還沒有嚥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向真一郎道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎沒有望向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他的視線卻避開了天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀察你之後就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是絕對不可能飛翔的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓能夠飛翔的真一郎為不能飛翔的你而煩惱太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣  太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以為是地說了這些話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你告訴我  我怎麼就不明白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你充滿了謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連和純之間的事也沒有告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴我  我就和你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始我們就不是什麼朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}還說那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那邊是不是打架啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}所以說你不能飛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖  女生之間打架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}別這樣  別這樣啦  比呂美冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}比呂美  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們兩個都不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我不明白的話  那希望你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話  不就沒法一起思考了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就沒法幫上真一郎的忙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想知道  真一郎的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到真一郎在煩惱  我真的很難過  痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻說我什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她  她該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會…你…喜歡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為只有你才能繼承雷轟丸的遺志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是那種喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪種喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  比如交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種戀愛方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美喜歡乃繪的老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是比呂美和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有模有樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他終於有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都表揚你的舞蹈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  上次要你讓我量了一下毛衣的肩寬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我織毛衣織得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  真一郎的毛衣也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女人  是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要和乃繪交往的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛  麻煩你先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和比呂美交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也和乃繪交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有做過那樣的承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你提出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能遵守承諾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會和比呂美分手的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要自以為是到什麼地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  你必須遵守承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往…  真一郎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  真一郎喜歡的應該不是那個叫乃繪的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（現在可以去你那邊吧  三代吉）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚特別的冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冷的地方眉來眼去  也別有情調的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  那件毛衣怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想快點穿上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友親手編織的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為這一輩子都無緣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是  不能幫你織
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了  小愛手很笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種地方正是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要對我那麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有資格享受三代吉你的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從真一郎那裡聽說  三代吉你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前  其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回到店裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  話還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你那下文  不知為何不想去聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是手牽手地回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛你是我的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於昨天的事  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你的事  幫我馬上改好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽又硬塞事情給你做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有從你媽媽那裡聽到些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有  什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪的事  讓我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為老是想著比呂美…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我認為我對乃繪是沒有戀愛感情的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡的話  也不會這樣受她折騰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是因為什麼交換條件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是昨天的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像開始戀愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何  好多地方都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很燙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉頰  胸口  耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…變了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:15:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得不好意思去見真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使改變了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不改變可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一節課是在別館  冬天真讓人冷到受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這樣冷  今晚絕對會下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能熬到今晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打賭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪也在下了  今天吃烏冬面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  昨天不也是吃的這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}那吃拉麵怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}拉麵好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}那決定咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三代吉  飯吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  我不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不  早飯吃多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀  那算了  找別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  如果是你的話  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…還是讓醫生去檢查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  今天沒有帶便當來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒有  沒有  沒…沒…有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你等一下吧  等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了的話你又會跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  還是想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「因為」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在生氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你為什麼逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼要追過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…有話對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話  快說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的話  我沒必要站住  說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限你三秒以內說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和…和…我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往？  什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是戀愛那方面的喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我喜歡你」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經找不到合適的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭不夠  明明還需要兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  會弄髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(650,200)}我喜歡乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在好想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢  明明不傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻特別地  特別地想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她  真的喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雪要積起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真的會感冒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  上次那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和乃繪交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像連我自己也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.71,0:21:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也看看我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不可以更加喜歡你？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.12,0:23:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝出一副乖乖女的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.30,0:23:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕易地俘獲男人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.59,0:23:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一場遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有下雪的小鎮
